6;Ayn: Beware evil eye of envy, perform ghusl","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe evil eye is real. If anything could precede the divine decree, it would be preceded by the evil eye. When you are asked to perform a ritual bath, then do so.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2188 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41842,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/02\/23\/gheebah-junnat-siyam\/","url_meta":{"origin":35660,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sawm: Lies and backbiting damage shield of fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 23, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting is a shield as long as you do not damage it.\u201d It was said, \u201cHow does one damage it?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cBy dishonesty or backbiting.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 4536 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2882,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/12\/dajjal-false-messiah-evil-good\/","url_meta":{"origin":35660,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dajjal: False Messiah says evil is good, good is evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"Ap